<p><strong>1.&nbsp;Agreement&nbsp;to&nbsp;Terms</strong></p><p>By&nbsp;accessing&nbsp;or&nbsp;using&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;(“we,”&nbsp;“our,”&nbsp;“us,”&nbsp;or&nbsp;“the&nbsp;Platform”),&nbsp;you&nbsp;agree&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;bound&nbsp;by&nbsp;these&nbsp;Terms&nbsp;of&nbsp;Service&nbsp;(“Terms”)&nbsp;and&nbsp;our&nbsp;Privacy&nbsp;Policy.&nbsp;If&nbsp;you&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;agree,&nbsp;you&nbsp;must&nbsp;stop&nbsp;using&nbsp;our&nbsp;services&nbsp;immediately.</p><p></p><p><strong>2.&nbsp;Nature&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Platform</strong></p><p>Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;cloud-based&nbsp;messaging&nbsp;and&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;platform&nbsp;that&nbsp;allows&nbsp;users&nbsp;to&nbsp;send&nbsp;SMS,&nbsp;MMS,&nbsp;and&nbsp;voice&nbsp;messages&nbsp;through&nbsp;carrier-approved&nbsp;channels.&nbsp;We&nbsp;act&nbsp;solely&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;technical&nbsp;service&nbsp;provider,&nbsp;not&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;publisher&nbsp;or&nbsp;originator&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;message&nbsp;content.&nbsp;You&nbsp;are&nbsp;solely&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;message&nbsp;content,&nbsp;recipient&nbsp;consent,&nbsp;and&nbsp;compliance&nbsp;with&nbsp;applicable&nbsp;laws.</p><p></p><p><strong>3.&nbsp;User&nbsp;Eligibility</strong></p><p>You&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;at&nbsp;least&nbsp;18&nbsp;years&nbsp;old&nbsp;to&nbsp;register&nbsp;or&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;platform.&nbsp;You&nbsp;agree&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;accurate&nbsp;and&nbsp;complete&nbsp;information&nbsp;and&nbsp;are&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;maintaining&nbsp;the&nbsp;confidentiality&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;credentials.&nbsp;All&nbsp;activities&nbsp;under&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;are&nbsp;your&nbsp;responsibility.</p><p></p><p><strong>4.&nbsp;Use&nbsp;of&nbsp;Services</strong></p><p>You&nbsp;agree&nbsp;to&nbsp;use&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;only&nbsp;for&nbsp;lawful&nbsp;business&nbsp;communication&nbsp;purposes.&nbsp;You&nbsp;may&nbsp;not&nbsp;use&nbsp;the&nbsp;service&nbsp;to:</p><p>-&nbsp;Send&nbsp;spam,&nbsp;phishing,&nbsp;or&nbsp;deceptive&nbsp;promotions</p><p>-&nbsp;Distribute&nbsp;sexually&nbsp;explicit,&nbsp;violent,&nbsp;or&nbsp;discriminatory&nbsp;content</p><p>-&nbsp;Violate&nbsp;carrier&nbsp;“SHAFT”&nbsp;restrictions&nbsp;(sex,&nbsp;hate,&nbsp;alcohol,&nbsp;firearms,&nbsp;tobacco)</p><p>-&nbsp;Send&nbsp;messages&nbsp;without&nbsp;valid&nbsp;consent&nbsp;from&nbsp;recipients</p><p>-&nbsp;Engage&nbsp;in&nbsp;fraud,&nbsp;hacking,&nbsp;or&nbsp;other&nbsp;abusive&nbsp;behavior</p><p>Violations&nbsp;may&nbsp;result&nbsp;in&nbsp;immediate&nbsp;suspension&nbsp;or&nbsp;termination&nbsp;of&nbsp;your&nbsp;account.</p><p></p><p><strong>5.&nbsp;Message&nbsp;Delivery&nbsp;and&nbsp;Fees</strong></p><p>Message&nbsp;delivery&nbsp;is&nbsp;handled&nbsp;through&nbsp;third-party&nbsp;carriers&nbsp;and&nbsp;aggregators.&nbsp;We&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;guarantee&nbsp;delivery&nbsp;or&nbsp;timing.&nbsp;Usage&nbsp;fees&nbsp;are&nbsp;billed&nbsp;based&nbsp;on&nbsp;your&nbsp;selected&nbsp;plan&nbsp;or&nbsp;message&nbsp;volume.&nbsp;All&nbsp;charges&nbsp;are&nbsp;non-refundable&nbsp;unless&nbsp;required&nbsp;by&nbsp;law.&nbsp;Taxes,&nbsp;surcharges,&nbsp;and&nbsp;carrier&nbsp;fees&nbsp;may&nbsp;apply.</p><p></p><p><strong>6.&nbsp;Account&nbsp;Suspension&nbsp;and&nbsp;Termination</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;may&nbsp;suspend&nbsp;or&nbsp;terminate&nbsp;your&nbsp;account&nbsp;without&nbsp;notice&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;violate&nbsp;these&nbsp;Terms,&nbsp;our&nbsp;Messaging&nbsp;Policy,&nbsp;or&nbsp;applicable&nbsp;laws,&nbsp;or&nbsp;if&nbsp;fraudulent&nbsp;or&nbsp;abusive&nbsp;activity&nbsp;is&nbsp;detected.&nbsp;Necessary&nbsp;data&nbsp;may&nbsp;be&nbsp;retained&nbsp;for&nbsp;compliance&nbsp;or&nbsp;legal&nbsp;obligations.</p><p></p><p><strong>7.&nbsp;Intellectual&nbsp;Property</strong></p><p>All&nbsp;platform&nbsp;content,&nbsp;software,&nbsp;trademarks,&nbsp;and&nbsp;technology&nbsp;belong&nbsp;to&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;or&nbsp;its&nbsp;licensors.&nbsp;You&nbsp;may&nbsp;not&nbsp;copy,&nbsp;modify,&nbsp;or&nbsp;redistribute&nbsp;any&nbsp;part&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;platform&nbsp;without&nbsp;written&nbsp;consent.</p><p></p><p><strong>8.&nbsp;Disclaimers</strong></p><p>The&nbsp;platform&nbsp;is&nbsp;provided&nbsp;“as&nbsp;is”&nbsp;and&nbsp;“as&nbsp;available,”&nbsp;without&nbsp;warranties&nbsp;of&nbsp;any&nbsp;kind.&nbsp;We&nbsp;do&nbsp;not&nbsp;guarantee&nbsp;uninterrupted&nbsp;service,&nbsp;delivery&nbsp;success,&nbsp;or&nbsp;error-free&nbsp;operation.&nbsp;Use&nbsp;the&nbsp;service&nbsp;at&nbsp;your&nbsp;own&nbsp;risk.</p><p></p><p><strong>9.&nbsp;Limitation&nbsp;of&nbsp;Liability</strong></p><p>To&nbsp;the&nbsp;maximum&nbsp;extent&nbsp;permitted&nbsp;by&nbsp;law,&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;is&nbsp;not&nbsp;liable&nbsp;for&nbsp;indirect,&nbsp;incidental,&nbsp;or&nbsp;consequential&nbsp;damages,&nbsp;including&nbsp;loss&nbsp;of&nbsp;profits,&nbsp;data,&nbsp;or&nbsp;goodwill,&nbsp;or&nbsp;for&nbsp;message&nbsp;delivery&nbsp;failures&nbsp;caused&nbsp;by&nbsp;carriers&nbsp;or&nbsp;third&nbsp;parties.&nbsp;Total&nbsp;liability&nbsp;shall&nbsp;not&nbsp;exceed&nbsp;the&nbsp;amount&nbsp;paid&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;service&nbsp;during&nbsp;the&nbsp;past&nbsp;3&nbsp;months.</p><p></p><p><strong>10.&nbsp;Indemnification</strong></p><p>You&nbsp;agree&nbsp;to&nbsp;indemnify&nbsp;and&nbsp;hold&nbsp;Group&nbsp;Direct&nbsp;Message&nbsp;harmless&nbsp;from&nbsp;any&nbsp;claims,&nbsp;penalties,&nbsp;or&nbsp;damages&nbsp;arising&nbsp;from&nbsp;your&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;service,&nbsp;message&nbsp;content,&nbsp;or&nbsp;violations&nbsp;of&nbsp;applicable&nbsp;laws&nbsp;or&nbsp;these&nbsp;Terms.</p><p></p><p><strong>11.&nbsp;Governing&nbsp;Law&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Dispute&nbsp;Resolution</strong></p><p>These&nbsp;Terms&nbsp;are&nbsp;governed&nbsp;by&nbsp;the&nbsp;laws&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;State&nbsp;of&nbsp;New&nbsp;York.&nbsp;Any&nbsp;dispute&nbsp;shall&nbsp;be&nbsp;resolved&nbsp;through&nbsp;binding&nbsp;arbitration&nbsp;in&nbsp;New&nbsp;York&nbsp;County,&nbsp;NY,&nbsp;under&nbsp;the&nbsp;rules&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;American&nbsp;Arbitration&nbsp;Association&nbsp;(AAA).</p><p></p><p><strong>12.&nbsp;Modifications&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;Terms</strong></p><p>We&nbsp;may&nbsp;update&nbsp;these&nbsp;Terms&nbsp;at&nbsp;any&nbsp;time.&nbsp;Updates&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;posted&nbsp;on&nbsp;www.groupdm.net.&nbsp;Continued&nbsp;use&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;platform&nbsp;constitutes&nbsp;acceptance&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;revised&nbsp;Terms.</p><p></p><p><strong>13.&nbsp;Contact</strong></p><p>For&nbsp;questions&nbsp;or&nbsp;concerns,&nbsp;please&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us&nbsp;at&nbsp;support@groupdm.net.</p><p></p>